      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "damage = mean(2^(T/10))\nT_eq = 10*log2(damage)\n以科威特市为 1.00x 基准。\n高温尾部会被指数放大。",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "damage = mean(2^(T/10))\nT_eq = 10*log2(damage)\n以科威特市为 1.00x 基准。\n高温尾部会被指数放大。",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 142
    },
